{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:01:03.396847+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've found the answer in `profiles.toml`, which defines the encoding profiles for the `vidpack` command. Here are the three selectable profiles:\n\n| Profile | Codec | Container | Key Settings |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **`web`** | **H.264** (libx264) video + **AAC** audio | **MP4** | 2 Mbit/s video bitrate, scaled to 1280×720 |\n| **`archive`** | **H.265/HEVC** (libx265) video + **FLAC** audio | **MKV** | CRF 18, source resolution (no scaling) |\n| **`gif`** | *(palette-based GIF)* | **GIF** | 12 fps, scaled to width 480 (aspect preserved) |\n\nSo in short:\n- **web** → H.264 in MP4 (streaming-friendly)\n- **archive** → H.265 in MKV (high-quality lossless-audio preservation)\n- **gif** → Animated GIF in GIF (lightweight, web-friendly animation)", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 268, "prompt_tokens": 3088, "total_tokens": 3356, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 16, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 2816, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0001210048, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 4.59648e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 7.504e-05}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780873253-d5WJHaMooSMqAVV51PD8", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea451-51e0-7462-b42d-e274ba35a94a-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 3088, "output_tokens": 268, "total_tokens": 3356, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2816}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 16}}}}]}}}
